**Simulated Problem**




Title: E-Commerce Revenue Forecast

Description: Generate daily sales data for 1 year for an online store. Let daily number of orders follow a Poisson distribution and average order value follow a normal distribution. Compute monthly revenues and identify months with unusually high or low performance.

